  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Oral BCX4161 as a Prophylactic Treatment for HAE</brief_title>
  <acronym>OPuS-1</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Double-Blind Placebo-Controlled 2-Period Crossover Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of BCX4161 as a Prophylactic Treatment to Reduce the Frequency of Attacks in Subjects With Hereditary Angioedema</official_title>
  <sponsors>
